data.value:
1. Hold your cube with the white face on top and the green face facing towards you.
2. Check that the white edges on your cube are in the EXACT same position as any one of the cubes in the diagram below (ignore the positioning of the corners). If they are not, perform U moves until they match.
3. Perform the following sequence of moves: F, R, U, R', U', F' (This will move the cube from one stage to the next, as shown in the diagram below).
4. Repeat steps 2 and 3 until the final stage in the diagram below is reached (far right).
